Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这花…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 现在我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到蓓儿丹蒂会受到停职处分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不能用法力了 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂不能再飞了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只有一星期啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是居然要一星期！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使恢复许可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须回天界再学习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人看无聊的录像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天做法术练习 真的很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是兀儿德那时候不是50年…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初犯是那种程度而已的 安心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一星期的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差不多该去大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是角田教授的课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一点都不介意的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:04.11,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HF8B356&}{\3c&H47E7F3&}啊啊 不管在哪里 只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来是有事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想寄放行李在你家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李？要寄放多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…一星期的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 兄弟们 他答应了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 因为宿舍改建 没地方放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会稍微有点不便 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微？这叫稍微？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些你打算怎么处理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别推在我头上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是一句话都没说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田宫是由你负责的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这谁规定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚规定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…算了 万一放不下就堆在大堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小萤 我又买了新的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在送去废品回收之前 冰箱 洗衣机 被炉 在你这儿放一放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 刚拍卖到两台超棒的罕见机车…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没地方放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理完车库我就会来拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这些硬纸板箱一起先在你这里寄放一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服买得太多 家里的仓库堆不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扩建完之前能不能在你家放一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用都放在我们家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 要是我没被停职
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把它们变小收起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 这件事交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把行李放在一起 然后我自有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…光是这样就够呛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来考考大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间没办法整理是因为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为空间不够？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 解决方法就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里到大堂已经满了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里同学 你有没有在听啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是“制造”空间 制·造
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间复制机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功能设为“扩大” 面积选择6倍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定 开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：这…这不是SFC的手柄吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？房间变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我制造了空间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造？怎么制造？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确切地说是预借
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时 两小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还是存在这这样的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那空间移到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间就会像是变多了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是太明白 不过感觉挺厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 空间是有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家开始整理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙逃走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 你这么说我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 有地方放就该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…要放在…哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬不动不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法术…不行 现在用的话 执照会被吊销的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这个放这边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一你好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我觉得这很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我无法使用法力 就变得如此无力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相比 萤一你真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先把中午以前能完成的搬完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 一下子就快装满了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再变大一点好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个是按这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是先选扩大模式再选面积吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个啊？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样设定！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附加项？有这东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是右边的按钮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 现在输入面积
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 现在气氛应该不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂！萤一！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 这个空间已经接近无限大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能听到我们的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限大…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口到底在哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到空间复制机居然失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器不能重设吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十字键按上上下下左右左右
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后按两次确定键
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得萤一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我去帮他们重设
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的 你打算怎么去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停职中的姐姐现在不能用法术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用法术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就感觉不到她的波动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能知道他们在哪里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是找不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确定的是他们在中心点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为空间复制机是以房间中心来扩大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是就容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 如果能知道中心点在哪儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个无限大的空间 要怎么找到中心？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这里是组合式的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦迷路就别想出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说没办法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 连方向都无法判断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么随便乱走也不是办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能因为停职不能使用法术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一你才是 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时一直被前辈们差来使去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有机会如此放松 就慢慢等救援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我并不讨厌这么无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来倒是我觉得无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找点事来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦 那么就做两个人能做的事 作为排遣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器用什么作动力？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要等电池用完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算蓓儿丹蒂没事 萤一就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 萤一一定能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有姐姐在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停职中的姐姐并不是不能用法术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说一旦发生什么还是可以用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子看到萤一有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会用法术的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失去女神的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…食物…啊 面（パスタ）！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,タ…タ…蛋（タマゴ）先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 不用加“先生”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是什么都喜欢加敬语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么接下来是动物 开始喽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用加“先生”了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到什么办法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里的时间往前调一星期的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做是做得出…就是要花六天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼吗 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再深一点喽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 挖出来了 接下来是另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个空间会持续多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时…两小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之诗寇蒂她们会想出办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果几天都是这样…萤一就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有过因为没钱一两天不吃东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我一定不能坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能眼睁睁看着那样的萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会使用法术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算无法再做女神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能救你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这么无法信任吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候真希望你多依赖我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们千万不能灰心 救援一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样坚信 就一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前为了能接近你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽量让自己不使用法术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时甚至会想 就算失去法术也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在却像缺少了什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禁止使用法力 让我再次认识到你的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我自己的软弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想 停职一星期没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对你们来说 却像是失去手足般痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 现在的我还能和平时没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要理解你的痛苦 或许根本是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…虽然我不会说什么安慰的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别忘了有我在你身边！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然帮不上什么忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我觉得非常有安全感！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓…蓓…蓓…蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 做两台缩短3天时间的机器如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话两天就能做一台了 只要4天就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话萤一应该能坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看着萤一的姐姐会受不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能用法术 但跳舞还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 以前曾经和沙夜子比赛过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我还不太会跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起运动会时候的土风舞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下哦 Lysanda
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的行李里面混进了这孩子的饲料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没那闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的行李呢？问森里或小蓓儿就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了现在没那闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 森里！初代部长大人来了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里和小蓓儿在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了现在没那闲工夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lysanda？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 洗澡水放好了 温度刚刚好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么我进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来为您搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先做好再来帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼先生～鱼先生～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我来为您搓背了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真舒服 真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的主菜是北欧产的高级的地道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真香 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 真好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过来我可就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我真是笨蛋！）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这个国王游戏让你更饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？无限远的天花板和墙壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是地板却近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个空间的下方不是无限的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 地板下方可能还是原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就用这个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一不是那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能会破坏空间 通向异界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要打开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其被困在这无限的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是去一个未知的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不管到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有蓓儿丹蒂…\N只要有萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二…三！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！异世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lysanda！在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊，Lysanda！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来森里好像不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就外带忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？刚才那是千寻学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的小猫是千寻小姐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做6台缩短一天时间的机器呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要半天就行了…好厉害 三天就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 外面也很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 我还是想做女神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一星期的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…如果一直不能使用法力…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样也能在我的身边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…萤一
